snippet.title: Thu Vu
snippet.description:
Hi there! Thanks for checking out my channel. Me in 3 words: Economist turned data nerd. I'm a Data science consultant by profession in the past 5 years, based in the Netherlands. My background is in Economics and Computer Science. I love learning and explaining stuff about data science. If that sounds interesting, consider subscribing! :)
